= WebresourcesParser

Given a webresources.xml file and a base url, these scripts will scan each url in your site and determine which styles are being used on each page (uses UrlParser).

= UrlParser

Given a url, this script will determine which styles are being used on the page.

= Installing

To install, just type:
`bundle install`

= Using

To use WebresourcesParser, type:
`./parse_webresources.rb <path_to_webresources.xml> <base_url>`

To use UrlParser, type:
`./parse_url.rb <url>`

